{"word":"G1890 - ἐπαφρίζω - epaphrízō - ep-af-rid'-zo - Foam out","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπαφρίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epaphrízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-af-rid'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Foam out</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நுரை தள்ளு"},{"paragraph":"to foam up to cast out as foam, foam out"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G875 - ἀφρίζω - aphrízō - af-rid'-zo/875\">G875</a>; to <i>foam upon</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>exhibit</i> (a vile passion): - foam out.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}